Tonight, the police are in hot pursuit of a 34-year-old police woman who is alleged to be behind the killings of two people both within 72 hours. Corporal Caroline Chemutai Kangongo, said to be highly skilled sharp shooter is still at large after committing the murders. Police have since declared corporal Kangongo as armed and dangerous and is believed to have shot dead the two men, one being a fellow police officer. Our reporter Ibrahim Karanja pieces together the last couple of hours in which the law offender turned into a fugitive.
